	<p pid="a.119.8/1">The review of public administration consultation process attracted 1,206 responses.</p>
	<p pid="a.119.8/2">The report <i>Future Post-Primary Arrangements in Northern Ireland&mdash;Advice from the Post-Primary Review Working Group</i>, widely known as the Costello report, was not published for consultation. The working group's remit was,</p>
	<p pid="a.119.8/3" class="indent">&quot;To take account of the responses to the consultation on the Burns Report, including the diversity of views on academic selection, and provide advice on options for future arrangements for post-primary education&quot;.</p>
	<p pid="a.119.8/4">In view of the advisory nature of its remit, its report was not published for consultation.</p>
</reply>
